PURPOSE
~~~~~~~
This program is designed to extract PalmOS font resources (NFNT) from
binary files. The extracted fonts are saved in two formats.
The first format is text, compatible with PilRC resource compiler.
The second format is binary, compatible with Pilot Font Editor.
Binary fonts could also be converted into PDB modules for Font Hack 123.


BASICS
~~~~~~
usage:  pilfont infile

infile  - the file containing the binary font data

The extracted fonts are saved under names:
fontWxH.txt - text format, compatible with PilRC
fontWxH.pft - binary format, compatible with Pilot Font Editor
